[SHORT DESC]
Ignores accuracy modifiers.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Faint Attack ignores all accuracy and evasion modifiers.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/shadow_punch">Shadow Punch</a> is a Ghost-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/rs/moves/faint_attack">Aerial Ace</a> is a Flying-type equivalent, though physical.<br />
<a href="/rs/moves/shock_wave">Shock Wave</a> is an Electric-type equivalent, but is special.<br />
<a href="/rs/moves/bite">Bite</a> is almost identical, but can miss if accuracy modifiers are present and has a chance to flinch.</p>